snippet.title: Snail against Squirrel for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Ugh, this game is horrible.

You have to get the bricks (whatever they are...probably food for the giant frog, lol) before they disappear.

The problem is, this food is automatically your life and they disappear way to fast, which especially is annoying if you are at the top.
